name: MobilenNetV2 SSD 300x300 Object Detector
description: Localize the most prominent object in theimage from a set of N categories such asCrosswalk, Green/Red signal, Car

input_tensor_metadata.name: Image
input_tensor_metadata.description: Input image to be classified. The expected image is 640 x 640, with three channels (red, blue, green) per pixel. Each value in the tensor is a single byte between 0 and 255.

output_tensor_metadata.name: location
output_tensor_metadata.description: The location of the detected boxes.

output_tensor_metadata.name: category
output_tensor_metadata.description: The categories of the detected boxes.

associated_files.name: labelmap.txt
associated_files.description: Label of objects that this model can recognize.

output_tensor_metadata.name: score
output_tensor_metadata.description: The score of the detected boxes.

output_tensor_metadata.name: number of detections
output_tensor_metadata.description: The number of the detected boxes.

author: Phoenix
